6. API 设计
登录
POST /api/v1/auth/login
{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}
添加服务器
POST /api/v1/servers
{
  "name": "web-01",
  "host": "1.2.3.4",
  "port": 22,
  "username": "root",
  "auth_type": "private_key"
}
部署防护规则
POST /api/v1/servers/{id}/deploy
添加黑名单 IP
POST /api/v1/firewall/blacklist
{
  "server_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "ip": "8.8.8.8",
  "timeout": 0,
  "reason": "manual block"
}
添加地区封禁
POST /api/v1/geo/block
{
  "server_ids": [1],
  "country": "CN",
  "province": "Guangdong",
  "enabled": true
}
查询 IP 地区
GET /api/v1/geo/search?ip=8.8.8.8

智能预览 CIDR
POST /api/v1/geo/cidrs/preview
{
  "cidrs": ["8.8.8.0/24", "1.1.1.0/24"]
}

部署默认地区白名单
POST /api/v1/geo/default-whitelist
{
  "server_ids": [1],
  "enabled": true,
  "country": "泰国",
  "cleanup": true
}

同步默认白名单 CIDR 并重部署
POST /api/v1/geo/default-whitelist/sync
{
  "server_ids": [1],
  "enabled": true,
  "strict_whitelist": true,
  "cleanup": true,
  "phase": "all"
}
phase 取值：cidr（仅更新本地 CIDR，无需 server_ids）| deploy | rule | all（默认，一次完成）

默认白名单自动同步配置
GET  /api/v1/geo/default-whitelist/auto-sync
PUT  /api/v1/geo/default-whitelist/auto-sync
{
  "enabled": true,
  "server_ids": [1, 2]
}

检测服务器防火墙规则是否生效
GET /api/v1/servers/{id}/firewall/status

返回：

{
  "server_id": 1,
  "mounted": true,
  "strict_whitelist": true,
  "strict_whitelist_active": true,
  "ipsets": [
    {"name": "cc_geo_whitelist", "exists": true, "entries": 17939}
  ],
  "iptables_rules": ["-A INPUT -m set --match-set cc_geo_whitelist src -j ACCEPT"],
  "iptables_counts": ["..."]
}

查询 IP 地区返回示例：

{
  "ip": "8.8.8.8",
  "country": "美国",
  "province": "加利福尼亚",
  "city": "Mountain View",
  "isp": "Google"
}
